{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_10_01",
  "title": "小美山愛 1話 私もBIG4ですからね",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そろそろ、愛との打ち合わせの時間だな\nおーい、愛、入るぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's about time for the meeting with Ai.\nHey‚ Ai‚ I'm coming in.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.3333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2900.0000000000005,
          "startTime": 3.7
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5066.6666667,
          "startTime": 5.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.8166666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.8166666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "……本当に、大丈夫だから\n心配しないで……うん、本当に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Really‚ I'm fine.\nDon't worry… yeah‚ really…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.3014673597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（電話中か。気付いてないみたいだな）\n（……ん？　愛、もしかして泣いてるのか……！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She's on the phone. Doesn't seem to notice me.）\n（…Hm? Ai‚ could she be crying…!?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "お父さん、ありがとう……負けないよ、私\nだって、BIG4になったんだもん……うん、またね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Dad‚ thank you… I won't lose.\nYou know‚ I’m part of the BIG4 now… yeah‚ talk to you later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-end-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10633.333333299997,
          "startTime": 36.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.9
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "……よっし、気合いを入れなさい小美山愛！\n元気！　笑顔！　筋肉！　しゃー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Alright‚ get fired up‚ Ai Komiyama!\nEnergy! Smile! Muscles! Haaa!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（い、今の掛け声はなんだ……？）\n（……とにかく、もう一度声を掛けてみるか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Wh-what was that cheer just now…?）\n（…Anyway‚ guess I’ll try calling to her again.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、愛？　打ち合わせの時間だけど……大丈夫か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Ai? It's time for our meeting… are you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.9666689555
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！　お疲れ様です\n今度の花火大会の件ですよね！　準備はばっちりです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san! Good work.\nIt's about the upcoming fireworks festival! I'm perfectly prepared.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、そうなんだけど……ところで愛\n何か悩みや困ったことがあれば、相談してほしいんだが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ that's right‚ but… by the way‚ Ai‚\nif you have any worries or troubles‚ I'd like you to consult with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.8153353352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.16667099
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "相談、ですか？　……何もないですよ？\nどうしたんですか、急に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Consultation? …There's nothing.\nWhat's wrong‚ all of a sudden?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.2333376567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（愛は、何かあったらすぐ相談してくれるんだけど……）\n（今回は、言い辛い悩みを抱えてるのかもしれないな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ai usually consults with me right away if something happens…）\n（This time‚ she might be holding onto troubles that are hard to talk about.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.26667099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.2000043233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いや、BIG4になって以来忙しいだろ？　だから心配\nしてたんだ。何かあれば、いつでも話を聞くからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ you've been busy since becoming BIG4‚ right? So I was worried\nabout you. If anything happens‚ I'm always here to listen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.4055335557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.6333376567
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "はい、頼りにしてます！\nえーと、じゃあ……会議を始めましょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ I'm counting on you!\nUm‚ well then… shall we start the meeting?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.1000043233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.1000043233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "出鼻を挫いてすまない\n今回の花火大会のステージは、元々はリズノワに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry to dampen your spirits right off the bat.\nThis fireworks festival stage was originally supposed to be for LizNoir…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.1333376567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（そうだ、この仕事は本来四人に来た仕事なんだけど）\n（愛しか都合が合わなかったんだよな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（That's right‚ this job was originally meant for all four of them‚ but）\n（only Ai was available…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.36667099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.1333376567
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、何か深刻そうな悩みごとを抱えてる愛に）\n（そんなネガティブな情報を伝えたら――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But if I tell Ai‚ who seems to be carrying some serious worries‚）\n（such negative information――）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.8333376567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.6333376567
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "えぇっ！？　わ、私一人……私だけ……\n私だけスケジュールに隙間があったんですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?! J-just me alone… only me…\nOnly I had a gap in my schedule…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.46667099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "どうせ私は余りものです……四天王なら最弱です……\nそんな余りもので隅っこの私が一人で行ったら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm just leftovers anyway… if I'm one of the Four Heavenly Kings‚ I'm the weakest…\nIf someone leftover and insignificant like me goes alone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.56667099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.6333386739
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "お客さん、帰っちゃうんじゃないですか……！？\n逆に、石を投げられて帰れって言われちゃうかも……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "won't the audience leave…!?\nOr worse‚ they might throw stones at me and tell me to go home…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.5520774855,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.2333376567
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "……さん？　……さーん！\n{user}さん！　大丈夫ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…-san? …-saaan!\n{user}-san! Are you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.36667099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.3999839783
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ。す、すまん、大丈夫だ\nえーと、どこまで話したんだったか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah. S-sorry‚ I'm fine.\nUm‚ where did I leave off…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.06667099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.4333173116
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんも葵さんもこころも、他に仕事があって\n移動時間を考えるとステージに間に合わないんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ Aoi-san‚ and Kokoro all have other work‚\nand considering travel time‚ they won't make it to the stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.1333376567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_01-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "だから私が一人で、という出演条件で\n先方にもご了承いただいた……で、合ってます？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So with the condition that I perform alone‚\nthe other party also agreed… is that right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.2666730245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
